         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 14 of Imperator Caesar Nerva Trajanus Augustus Germanicus Dacicus. Work done for 5 days on the dike works for the same year 14 at the desert canal, from Pachon 28 till Payni 2, on behalf of Tebtunis, Herak-- son of N.N. the son of Herak(), his mother being N.N. (2nd h.) Signature.</ab>
